For example, this works. req.query.region will return region: value [e.g. "DE"]

```&lt;select form="select-country" id="countries" name="region" class="form-control"&gt;
  &lt;option value="DE"&gt;Germany&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="US"&gt;United States&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;form id="select-country" action="/upcoming" method="GET"&gt;
  &lt;input type="submit" value="Upcoming Films" /&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;```

```&lt;form id="someId" action="/upcoming" method="GET"&gt;
&lt;select form="someId" id="region" name="region" class="form-control"&gt;
  &lt;option value="DE"&gt;Germany&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="US"&gt;United States&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Select a language:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;select form="someId" id="language" name="language" class="form-control"&gt;
  &lt;option value="de"&gt;German&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="en-US"&gt;English (US)&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
  &lt;input type="submit" value="Upcoming Films" /&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;```

